snippet.title: Neverwinter Nights 2: Complete trailer
snippet.description:
✅ Link to the game 👉  http://bit.ly/2DQWjK8

Welcome back to Neverwinter! Bards sing tales of heroes in ages past, but they rarely mention those that are yet to become heroes. One such hero is a farmer in the small village of West Harbor. Raised by the elven ranger, Daeghun, as his own child, our hero will embark on a grandiose quest against the King of Shadows. Neverwinter Nights 2 is the tale of his deeds.
